sys_ui_annotation.text: 1. Software Details
2. Scope Details

3. Are any special software features or options required to meet the business use case (i.e. does the software install a local database, provide an interface for other systems to connect or access the software or data, any other special options or functional capabilities)?
4. Will the software be used to export data anywhere outside of the system it is installed on?
5. Will the use of this software be temporary or permanent (if temporary, until what date)?
*6. What type of system will the software run on (user desktop/laptop/VDI, Server (Multi-user), lab device, mobile device, tablet, etc.)? Please provide the computer name(s).
7. Is the software running on a desktop system used/shared by more than one user?
8. Will the software be installed and run from a production or non-production (e.g. development, test, etc.) system/server? If yes, please provide server name(s) if available
9. Will the software be installed and run from a desktop/laptop/VDI? OR from a separate host (system other than a desktop/laptop/VDI)? OR from portable media (CD/DVD, USB)?
10. Please provide desktop/laptop/VDI hostname(s).
11. Will the software be installed on a Gilead regulated system (GxP, SOX, etc.)?
12. Will the software be used to connect to or access a Gilead regulated (GxP) system?
13. Does the user(s) of this software have access to Gilead regulated (GxP, SOX, etc.) data as part of their job requirement?
14. Will the software be used to access and/or (consume) Gilead "Sensitive" or "Confidential" data?
15. Does the software allow users to transport (upload) Gilead data to resources outside of Gilead (e.g. business partner, third party, service provider, etc.)?
16. Will the software be used to connect to or access a non-Gilead system (internal or external to Gilead)?
17. Does the software require access to the internet (or non-Gilead external network) for any reason?
18. Will the system(s) the software runs on have access to the internet (or non-Gilead external network)?
19. Will the system(s) the software runs on have access to Gilead's internal network only?
20. Will the system(s) the software runs on have no network connectivity (stand alone)?
